Session descriptions
Session 1
The first session was focused on obtaining the couple's individual and relationship history and explor-
ing potential goals for therapy. When asked what the couple would like to work on in therapy, Everett 
explained, “I am not very emotionally aware of how my behavior always affects her. So, I would like 
